Place cured venison, beans, water, and onion salt in slow cooker. Cook on low setting 3 1/2 hours. Remove venison from the slow cooker. Cut into bite size-pieces; discard bones. Transfer meat back to slow cooker and cook until tender, about 30 more minutes. Prepare Idahoan Signatureâ„¢ Russets Mashed Potatoes according to package instructions and serve along with the venison and beans.